 the CPV could also be directly\ndetected via the diphoton spectrum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Jun 2017 18:00:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 15 Jul 2017 19:37:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 3 Nov 2017 17:59:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-15"}
