rformance of\nengineered features in BC scenes and increase the accuracy by up to 8% in DO\nscenes. In addition, the overall pose history summarization tracing accuracy\nshows an average detection rate of 85% in BC and of 76% in DO scenes. The\nproposed keyframe estimation algorithm allows DECU to reach an average 78%\ntransition classification accuracy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Jun 2017 18:08:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-30"}
