combined with the requirement of entanglement wedge nesting. Our methods were,\nas such, designed as a precise probe of the RT surface close to the boundary of\na putative gravitational/stringy dual of \\emph{any} QFT with an interacting UV\nfixed point. We also prove a higher spin version of the QNEC.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Jun 2017 18:15:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Mar 2019 03:57:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-04"}
