lity, and disruption by stellar\nfeedback. At redshift z >~ 2, the Toomre instability timescale decreases,\nresulting in a prediction of higher molecular gas fractions at early times, in\nagreement with observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Jun 2017 03:18:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Jul 2017 09:07:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 2 Sep 2017 11:20:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-04"}
